Hola! I am loving #workfromhomelife so much! Feeling so much more productive in terms of keeping up with my workouts and my assignments on hand! Plus, eating home = eating healthy (most of the time) so life is good, I feel blessed and healthy! 
Those who attended my #livestream session this morning, let me know in the comments how you've enjoyed it!? I can't see the full video because I wasn't the host so I didn't get to see everyone who joined as well! But according to the screenshots and photos sent, I'm heartened to see so many of you guys! Special shoutout to my regular Saturday hot yogis, I miss you all too! Definitely going to host this again (probably longer session next time), especially so for my hot yogis!🤪🤪 @parve_kaur @sandraischiuy @omzjessy @shanyi_liew @vvviviennn @gohelynn @amittto @venusvernyce_ @huislu @_cheongtai #stayhomesg #stayhomeforsg

@huiyiingc no the video was not full. It was 5 min haha but maybe it's just not allowed I guess that's why corrupted? But yesterday when I downloaded the video right after the live, the full video was saved lol
I love it! 😍😍 Did you get the full video from Vanessa?
@unbelievaboy bet it was the best savasana ever🤪
hahah tbh i just wokeup and was shavasana throughout 🤪
@berrywhamdani HAHAHA glad you had fun though! Can always try the other modifications and slowly learn!😍
Haha I'm late for 10mins😆 can't follow the difficult techniques tough but overall was good.. 👍🏻
@_cheongtai thank you Cheongtai!!😍😍 super happy the sound was clear and all! Next week next week!
Eugene n I enjoyed it.  Yes, we look forward to next longer session 🤪
@grittygilly thank you Gillian!!! And you too! Loving all your amazing grooves and motivational posts😍😍😍
